745/https://sg.news.yahoo.com/structure-highway-construction-collapses-near-pie-leaving-1-dead-10-injured-002811390.html|archive-date=12 August 2017|url-status=live|language=en-SG|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/uncompleted-viaduct-near-pie-collapses-1-dead-10-injured-9030432|title=Uncompleted viaduct near PIE collapses; 1 dead, 10 injured|date=14 July 2017|work=Channel NewsAsia|access-date=21 October 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021111950/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/uncompleted-viaduct-near-pie-collapses-1-dead-10-injured-9030432|archive-date=21 October 2017|url-status=live|language=en-GB|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* 17 July \u2013 The Pioneer Polyclinic opens, the first polyclinic to be built in more than 10 years.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/new-polyclinic-opens-in-jurong-west|title=New polyclinic opens in Jurong West |publisher=The Straits Times|date=27 July 2017|accessdate=12 July 2019}}</ref>\n* 18 July \u2013 [[Tengah Air Base]] will be expanded to accommodate the relocation of [[Paya Lebar Air Base]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/tengah-air-base-to-be-expanded-more-than-80000-graves-exhumed-four-farms-to-be|title=Tengah Air Base to be expanded; more than 80,000 graves exhumed, 4 farms to be acquired|date=18 July 2017|work=The Straits Times|access-date=4 May 2019|language=en-SG}}</ref>\n* 22 July \u2013 Comic writer [[Sonny Liew]] wins 3 [[Eisner Award]]s for [[The Art of Charlie Chan Hock Chye]],<ref>{{Cite web |last1=Ho |first1=Olivia |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/graphic-novelist-sonny-liew-becomes-first-singaporean-to-win-eisner-award |title=Graphic novelist Sonny Liew is first Singaporean to win Eisner award, bagging 3 comics Oscars |website=The Straits Times |access-date=6 May 2019 |date=22 July 2017}}</ref> 2 years after the [[National Arts Council, Singapore|National Arts Council]] (NAC) withdre