om/news/singapore/nsf-death-armoured-vehicle-lands-on-side-while-getting-out-of-9223014|title=NSF death: Armoured vehicle lands on side while getting out of difficult terrain, says MINDEF|website=Channel NewsAsia|date=16 September 2017|accessdate=5 May 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127112044/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/nsf-death-armoured-vehicle-lands-on-side-while-getting-out-of-9223014|archivedate=27 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-09-16/singapore-army-officer-dies-on-queensland-coast/8953582|title=Singapore Army officer dies in armoured vehicle crash on Queensland coast|website=ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation)|date=16 September 2017|accessdate=5 May 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214164501/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-09-16/singapore-army-officer-dies-on-queensland-coast/8953582|archivedate=14 February 2018}}</ref> it was the [[List of military training deaths in Singapore|first death case relating to military training]] in almost five years.\n**[[SMRT Trains]] is appointed the operator of the [[Thomson\u2013East Coast MRT line]] for an initial 9 years.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lta.gov.sg/apps/news/page.aspx?c=2&id=3c9fa6b9-f21c-4444-9a1f-9be87397ab53|title=SMRT Trains Appointed to Operate the Thomson\u2013East Coast Line|date=15 September 2017|publisher=Land Transport Authority}}</ref>\n*23 September - An Asia Fighting Championship match between Pradip Subramanian and Steven Lim turns tragic, leading to the former's death.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Chia |first1=Alvin |title=Tragedy strikes at Asia Fighting Championship as bodybuilder Pradip Subramanian dies |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/sport/tragedy-strikes-at-asia-fighting-championship-as-bodybuilder-pradip-subramanian-32-dies |website=The Straits Times |accessdate=31 December 2019 |date=24 September 2017}}</ref>\n*29 September \u2013 [[Today (Singapore newspap