a-signs-agreement-with-bike-sharing-firms-nparks-town-councils-on-responsible |website=The Straits Times |accessdate=10 August 2019 |date=5 October 2017}}</ref>\n* 7 October \u2013 A major disruption of train services between Ang Mo Kio and Newton lasted 21 hours due to [[Bishan tunnel flooding|flooding]] in the MRT tunnels of the North South Line, caused by a malfunctioned pump.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/flooded-mrt-tunnel-trackside-fire-caused-train-disruption-on-nsl-9289414 |title=Flooded MRT tunnel, trackside fire caused train disruption on NSL: SMRT |website=Channel NewsAsia |access-date=21 October 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015150830/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/flooded-mrt-tunnel-trackside-fire-caused-train-disruption-on-nsl-9289414 |archive-date=15 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last1=Sin |first1=Yuen |url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/transport/problem-with-water-pumps-behind-mrt-disruption |title=Problem with water pumps behind North-South Line disruption over weekend |website=The Straits Times |access-date=21 October 2017 |date=9 October 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021183843/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/transport/problem-with-water-pumps-behind-mrt-disruption |archive-date=21 October 2017}}</ref>\n* 8 October - Singaporean singer [[Joanna Dong]] finishes third in [[Sing! China (season 2)]].<ref>{{cite web |last1=Singh |first1=Bryna |title=Singaporean singer Joanna Dong emerges second runner-up in Sing! China finals |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/singaporean-singer-joanna-dong-is-out-of-grand-finals-of-sing-china |website=The Straits Times |access-date=29 September 2019 |date=8 October 2017}}</ref>\n* 9 October \u2013 [[Singapore Post|SingPost]] Centre reopens with after two years of retrofitting works.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.singpost.com/about-us/news-releases/singpost-centre-new-one-stop-lifestyle-destinatio